{"word":"ἐριστός","slug":"ἐριστός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n42539\" key=\"e)risto/s\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἐριστ-ός</orth>,, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ή</itype>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">όν</itype>, <sense id=\"n42539.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">that may be contested,</tr_> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τὰ δὲ τοῖς δυνατοῖς οὐκ ἐριστὰ πλάθειν</foreign> such <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">contests can</tr_>not <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">be waged</tr_> with the powerful, so as to engage with them, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg005.perseus-grc1:220\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ El.\">El.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">220</biblScope> </bibl> (lyr.).</sense> </entryFree>"}]}